0w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/manchester_co_op-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/manchester_co_op-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/manchester_co_op-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/manchester_co_op-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/manchester_co_op-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3753533" class="wp-caption-text">曼彻斯特的合作社现场竞技场。图片来源：彼得·伯恩/PA图像/盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>在辞职之前，加里·罗登（Gary Roden）驳回了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-case-has-been-made-for-a-1-ticket-levy-on-all-arena-gigs-for-the-survival-of-grassroots-venues-and-artists-3611533">所有演出竞技场大小及以上的票务征收征收的呼吁</a>，这被建议确保英国较小的场地的未来。他还指出，某些基层场所“跑步不佳”，他提出了争议。</p><p>作为回应， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-say-manchester-co-op-live-arena-comments-were-disrespectful-and-disingenuous-and-call-on-1-ticket-levy-to-save-uk-talent-pipeline-3749732">MVT首席执行官马克·戴维德（Mark Davyd）告诉<em>NME</em> ，他认为罗登的言论“是无礼和不明智的”</a> 。在本周，合作社Live Arena被迫在许多后勤问题之后被迫推迟其发布会的一周，他喊出具有讽刺<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-hit-back-at-manchesters-co-op-live-for-saying-some-grassroots-venues-are-poorly-run-despite-arena-facing-own-major-issues-3749643">意味的“不必要，不必要和误导”的评论</a>。</p><p>戴维德（Davyd）说，最初，新的竞技场“拒绝邀请邀请到有关英国现场音乐生态系统未来的讨论”。</p><p>计划在曼彻斯特的合作社现场表演的其他表演包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-black-keys">《黑钥匙》</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eric-clapton">《埃里克·克拉普顿》</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicki-minaj">《尼基·米娜》</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eagles">老鹰</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pet-shop-boys">宠物店男孩</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">杀手</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elbow-are-ready-to-open-manchesters-co-op-live-arena-tonight-after-weeks-of-chaos-see-you-there-3755979">经过数周的混乱之后，肘部肘部已准备就绪，今晚打开曼彻斯特的合作现场竞技场：“见到你在那里”</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
